  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. Grill beef strips for 3-4 minutes per side, or until cooked to desired level of doneness.",
    "3. Meanwhile, toast tortilla wraps by wrapping them in foil and heating in the oven at 350°F for 5 minutes.",
    "4. Assemble wraps by spreading a layer of feta cheese on each tortilla, followed by a few slices of grilled beef, some crunchy slaw, lettuce, tomatoes, and red onion.",
    "5. Drizzle with lemon juice and olive oil, and top with kalamata olives.",
    "6. Serve immediately and enjoy!"
